OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMicrosoft cleared for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbiggest ever gaming deal   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Microsoft's revised offer to buy Call  
OL,6, of Duty-maker Activision Blizzard has  
OL,7, been approved by UK regulators.        
OL,9,FThe Competition and Markets Authority  
OL,10,Fsaid the deal addressed its concerns,  
OL,11,Fafter the watchdog blocked the original
OL,12,F$69bn (#59bn) bid in April.            
OL,14,FThe green light marks the culmination  
OL,15,Fof a near two-year fight to secure the 
OL,16,Fgaming industry's biggest-ever         
OL,17,Ftakeover.                              
OL,19,FBut despite approving the takeover, the
OL,20,FCMA criticised Microsoft's conduct.    
